GDE2 Utilities
===============================================================================

GDE2 Utilities for the GDE2 Desktop contains the following:

        gde2-system-log          [logview]
        gde2-search-tool         [gseachtool]
        gde2-dictionary          [gde2-dictionary]
        gde2-screenshot          [gde2-screenshot]
        gde2-disk-usage-analyzer [baobab]

This is a fork of GNOME Utilities.

Requirements:

        intltool                 >= 0.50.1
        gde2-common              >= 1.10.0
        glib                     >= 2.36.0
        gio                      >= 2.36.0
        gtk+                     >= 2.24.0
        libgde2-panel-applet     >= 1.7.0
        libgtop                  >= 2.12.0
        libcanberra-gtk          >= 0.4

The following configure flags can be used:

  --enable-zlib                   Enable ZLib support for Logview [default=yes]
  --with-grep                     Specify the path to the grep
                                  command [default=find it ourselves]
  --enable-debug                  Enable debug messages [default=no]
